<h1>Confirm your attendance for <%= @event.name %></h1>

<p>
Dear <%= @attendee.name %>,
</p>
<%= @message %> 

<p>Click one of the buttons below:</p>

<a class="button blue" href="https://eventbrite-rsvp.herokuapp.com/events/<%= @event.id %>/rsvp?email=<%= @attendee.email %>&token=<%= @attendee.digest %>&event_uid=<%= @event.uid %>&status=true" target="_blank">I am attending</a>

<a class="button red" href="https://eventbrite-rsvp.herokuapp.com/events/<%= @event.id %>/rsvp?email=<%= @attendee.email %>&token=<%= @attendee.digest %>&event_uid=<%= @event.uid %>&status=false" target="_blank">I am not attending</a>

<p>If the buttons didn't work, please copy-paste the link below:</p>
<p>If you are attending: https://eventbrite-rsvp.herokuapp.com/events/<%= @event.id %>/rsvp?email=<%= @attendee.email %>&token=<%= @attendee.digest %>&event_uid=<%= @event.uid %>&status=true</p>
<br><br>
<p>If you are not attending: https://eventbrite-rsvp.herokuapp.com/events/<%= @event.id %>/rsvp?email=<%= @attendee.email %>&token=<%= @attendee.digest %>&event_uid=<%= @event.uid %>&status=false</p>